        "tab_whats_inside": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What's Inside — And Why",
            "content": "<p>Every can carries our <strong>BRAiNLUBE Energy Blend</strong>, chosen so each piece pulls its weight:</p><ul><li><strong>Clean energy:</strong> natural caffeine (130mg from all sources), guarana, green coffee bean, and taurine for a lift without the sugar-bomb spike.</li><li><strong>Focus &amp; clarity:</strong> L-theanine + L-tyrosine, plus bacopa monnieri and ginkgo biloba — the nootropic side that supports memory, attention, and smooth thinking. The L-theanine is the quiet MVP: paired with caffeine, it is one of the most well-documented ways to get alert focus <em>without</em> the jitters or the crash.</li><li><strong>Calm &amp; resilience:</strong> ashwagandha and ginseng — adaptogens that help your body handle stress instead of adding to it.</li><li><strong>Full-spectrum support:</strong> rounded out with Vitamins C, D3, E, B6 &amp; B12, Niacin, Thiamin, Riboflavin, Pantothenic Acid, Magnesium, and Zinc.</li></ul><p>100% plant-based — no animal products, ever. No proprietary hand-waving — check the Supplement Facts panel in the product images for the full ingredient breakdown.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "open_as_drawer": false,
            "icon": "icon-zap",
            "margin_top": 0
          }
        },
        "tab_vitamins_minerals": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Vitamins & Minerals",
            "content": "<p>Beyond the Energy Blend, every can rounds things out with a full spread of vitamins and minerals:</p><ul><li>Vitamin C, D3 &amp; E</li><li>Vitamin B6 &amp; B12</li><li>Niacin, Thiamin HCl &amp; Riboflavin</li><li>Pantothenic Acid</li><li>Magnesium Citrate</li><li>Zinc Gluconate</li></ul><p>100% plant-based — no animal products, ever.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "open_as_drawer": false,
            "icon": "icon-plant",
            "margin_top": 0
          }
        },
        "tab_what_youll_feel": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What You'll Feel",
            "content": "<ul><li><strong>A clean lift</strong> — alert in about 20 minutes, no chest-pounding jolt.</li><li><strong>Locked-in focus</strong> — the kind of clarity where the noise fades and the work gets easier.</li><li><strong>Calm, not wired</strong> — adaptogens keep the edge off while the caffeine keeps you sharp.</li><li><strong>A smooth landing</strong> — steady energy that tapers instead of collapsing into a crash.</li></ul>",
