        "hotspot_Lfh9zF": {
          "type": "hotspot",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Ashwagandha",
            "title_position": "left",
            "vertical_position": 30,
            "horizontal_position": 39,
            "text": "<p><strong>Ashwagandha</strong> — <em>The calm inside your focus.<br/></em>An ancient adaptogen root built for modern stress. Ashwagandha helps your body stay calm under pressure, so your focus doesn't get hijacked by a racing mind. It's a big reason BRAiNLUBE's energy feels steady instead of frantic. Clarity and calm, working the same shift.</p>",
            "media_type": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/ashwagandha.jpg",
            "external_video_url": "",
            "external_video_aspect_ratio": "16:9",
            "video_controls": false,
            "video_autoplay": true
          }
        },
        "hotspot_kzmdRM": {
          "type": "hotspot",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Bacopa Monnieri",
            "title_position": "left",
            "vertical_position": 50,
            "horizontal_position": 39,
            "text": "<p><strong>Bacopa Monnieri</strong> — <em>The remembering herb.</em></p><p><br/>The student's herb. Bacopa has both a long traditional track record and modern research behind it for supporting memory and helping your brain hold on to what it learns. It also leans calming, taking the edge off stress while it works. Better retention, less overwhelm — that's why it's in every can.<br/></p>",
            "media_type": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/bacopamonnieri.jpg",
            "external_video_url": "",
            "external_video_aspect_ratio": "16:9",
            "video_controls": false,
            "video_autoplay": true
          }
        },
        "hotspot_P3diAL": {
          "type": "hotspot",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Caffeine",
            "title_position": "left",
            "vertical_position": 70,
            "horizontal_position": 39,
            "text": "<p><strong>Caffeine</strong> — <em>The lift, without the letdown.</em></p><p>The one you already know — done right. BRAiNLUBE uses a moderate 130mg (about a strong coffee) for real alertness without the overload. The trick is pairing it with L-theanine, which smooths the ride into calm, focused energy instead of jitters. You get the lift, not the letdown<br/></p>",
            "media_type": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Caffeine.jpg",
            "external_video_url": "",
            "external_video_aspect_ratio": "16:9",
            "video_controls": false,
            "video_autoplay": true
          }
        },
        "hotspot_nRCWcf": {
          "type": "hotspot",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Ginkgo Biloba",
            "title_position": "right",
            "vertical_position": 30,
            "horizontal_position": 60,
            "text": "<p><strong>Ginkgo Biloba</strong> — <em>Ancient tree, modern clarity.</em><br/>One of the oldest tree species on earth — and one of the most-studied brain botanicals. Ginkgo is prized for supporting healthy blood flow to the brain, which ties to sharper memory and steadier mental performance. In BRAiNLUBE, it's here to keep you quick on your feet, word after word, hour after hour.</p>",
            "media_type": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Caffeine_1.jpg",
            "external_video_url": "",
            "external_video_aspect_ratio": "16:9",
            "video_controls": false,
            "video_autoplay": true
          }
        },
        "hotspot_dpULtF": {
          "type": "hotspot",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Ginseng",
            "title_position": "right",
            "vertical_position": 50,
            "horizontal_position": 60,
            "text": "<p><strong>Ginseng</strong> — <em>Get-up-and-go, minus the jitters.</em><br/>A legendary adaptogen that wakes up mind and body at once. Ginseng helps support the brain chemistry behind focus and drive while helping you push back on fatigue and stress. It's the classic get-up-and-go root — without the jittery edge. In BRAiNLUBE, it keeps your mental engine running clean.</p>",
            "media_type": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Ginseng.jpg",
            "external_video_url": "",
            "external_video_aspect_ratio": "16:9",
            "video_controls": false,
            "video_autoplay": true
          }
        },
        "hotspot_jqmMnM": {
          "type": "hotspot",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Guarana",
            "title_position": "right",
            "vertical_position": 70,
            "horizontal_position": 60,
            "text": "<p><strong>Guarana</strong> — <em>Slow-burn energy from the Amazon.<br/></em><br/>An Amazonian berry and one of nature's richest sources of caffeine. Guarana tends to release its energy more slowly than coffee, for a smoother, longer-lasting lift. Traditionally used to boost mental energy and stamina, it's how BRAiNLUBE keeps you going without a hard drop-off. Clean fuel, steady burn.</p>",
            "media_type": "image",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Guarana.jpg",
            "external_video_url": "",
            "external_video_aspect_ratio": "16:9",
            "video_controls": false,
            "video_autoplay": true
          }
        }
